SUMMARY:Week 8: Estimating the Cost of Capital (Gold Cohort)
DESCRIPTION:Topic: Estimating the Cost of Capital\n\nObjectives:\n1. Estimate cost of equity using CAPM.\n2. Calculate WACC using costs of equity and debt.\n3. Apply WACC as discount rate for corporate investment projects.\n\nPre-Class Reading: Berk & DeMarzo (6th Ed.)\, Chapter 12\n\nAssignments Due This Week:\n- Homework 4: Wed May 6 @ 11:59pm\n- Ameritrade Case Study: Fri May 8 @ 11:59pm\n\nWeek 8 Page: https://bcourses.berkeley.edu/courses/1549853/pages/week-8\nAmeritrade Assignment: https://bcourses.berkeley.edu/courses/1549853/assignments/9059527\nHomework 4: https://bcourses.berkeley.edu/courses/1549853/assignments/9006400\nStudy.Net (Ameritrade PDF+Spreadsheet): https://bcourses.berkeley.edu/courses/1549853/external_tools/79374\nAll Assignments: https://bcourses.berkeley.edu/courses/1549853/assignments\nSyllabus: https://bcourses.berkeley.edu/courses/1549853/assignments/syllabus
